@startuml
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> Processing : URL submitted
Processing --> FeatureExtraction : Start feature extraction
FeatureExtraction --> URLNetProcessing : Features extracted
URLNetProcessing --> TransformerProcessing : URLNet prediction complete
TransformerProcessing --> ResultAggregation : Transformer prediction complete
ResultAggregation --> DecisionMade : Results combined
DecisionMade --> Phishing : Classified as phishing
DecisionMade --> Legitimate : Classified as legitimate
Phishing --> ReportGeneration : Generate detailed report
Legitimate --> ReportGeneration : Generate detailed report
ReportGeneration --> ResultsReady : Report completed
ResultsReady --> DisplayResults : Show to user
DisplayResults --> Idle : Results displayed

Idle : Waiting for URL input
Processing : Processing URL
FeatureExtraction : Extracting URL features
URLNetProcessing : Processing with URLNet model
TransformerProcessing : Processing with Transformer model
ResultAggregation : Combining model predictions
DecisionMade : Making final classification
Phishing : URL classified as phishing
Legitimate : URL classified as legitimate
ReportGeneration : Generating detailed analysis
ResultsReady : Analysis complete
DisplayResults : Showing results to user

note right of Processing
  System validates
  URL format and
  prepares for
  analysis
end note

note right of DecisionMade
  Ensemble decision
  based on both
  model predictions
end note
@enduml